<bibRefCitation author="Stock" box="[802,950,444,470]" pageId="5" pageNumber="12" refString="Stock, J. H. (1991) Pycnogonida of the MUSORSTOM campaigns to the Philippines. In: Crosnier, A. (Ed.), Resultats des Campagnes MUSORSTOM, Vol 8. Memoires du Museum national d'Histoire naturelle, Paris (A), 151, 213 - 228." type="journal article" year="1991">
